          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          To lead the world in premium laptop solutions, celebrated for innovation, quality, and an unwavering commitment to unlocking human potential through technology.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 py-20">
