      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 animate-fadeIn">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slideUp">
          From Silicon Valley roots to global impact, InfinityTech has redefined laptop excellence for over a decade—balancing power, portability, and stunning design.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
